snippet.title: Howloween Hero - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Howloween Hero is a wholesome Halloween adventure game about an adorable dog going trick or treating for their human.
Coming to Steam & iOS October 25th : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1715160/Howloween_Hero/
